NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, as to Elizabeth's choices for a rebid. First, it is a hard hand to bid. Bidding 3D takes up a lot of room, so she needs to have a good idea of where the hand is going, or a strong enough hand to handle a 4 level bid. The other choices are 3C and 3H. She has only 2 card support, but the best possible support she can have. In either cases she should pass 3NT.|
